name: Mentalhelp
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: mental quote
des: This Alexa skill automatically generates a reassuring quote targeted towards people with anxiety. No matter who you are you'll enjoy this skill with quotes being added all the time you'll greet your day with a positive upbeat attitude, don't let anxiety get in your way it's your life and you control it. Disclaimer: I am not an expert on any mental health disorders nor is this skill a substitute for any sort of professional treatment including a therapist, please call 1-800-273-8255 if your experiencing depression or suicidal thoughts or reach out to a mental health doctor or therapist
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
